Cell["\<\
Calculate the entanglement entropy (EE) averaged over different trajectories \
of quantum states.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->2072972421,ExpressionUUID->"6b5c12b8-6540-4ada-9694-c09fb92361d5"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

